          </m:msub>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>10</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </equation>
    <para id="id181160">Determine the distribution for <emphasis effect="italics">X</emphasis>. What are the probabilities Ellen loses money,
breaks even, or comes out ahead?</para>
</problem>
